# üêû bug report

The issue is caused by package `@angular/core`

### Description

It's not possible to use `@HostBinding` for class attribute on an SVG element.

This does not work:

```
  @HostBinding('class')
  get statusCode() {
    return this.mapElement.status.code
  }
```

This works:

```
<svg:g class="statusCode">
     <rect width="20" height="20" />
</svg:g>
```


